{"id":608168,"link":"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/2019/03/【立此存照】在《鲁迅研究》课程发表损害国家声/","date":"2019-03-28T10:07:14Z","modified":"2019-03-28T10:07:14Z","title":"【立此存照】在《鲁迅研究》课程发表损害国家声誉言论","content":"<p>近日，网传一份《重庆师范大学关于撤销唐云教师资格并给予降低岗位等级处分的决定》。决定书称该校文学院的唐云教师在《鲁迅研究》课程教学中，发表了损害国家声誉言论，违反政治纪律，严重违法教师职业道德等，最终校方决定给予降低岗位等级行政处分。</p>\n<p><img class=\"aligncenter wp-image-608169\" src=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2019/03/D2vCT6KU4AA8YGo.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"500\" height=\"667\" srcset=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2019/03/D2vCT6KU4AA8YGo.jpg 900w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2019/03/D2vCT6KU4AA8YGo-225x300.jpg 225w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2019/03/D2vCT6KU4AA8YGo-768x1024.jpg 768w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 500px) 100vw, 500px\" /> <img class=\"aligncenter wp-image-608170\" src=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2019/03/D2vCV_2VYAAlETW.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"500\" height=\"667\" srcset=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2019/03/D2vCV_2VYAAlETW.jpg 900w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2019/03/D2vCV_2VYAAlETW-225x300.jpg 225w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2019/03/D2vCV_2VYAAlETW-768x1024.jpg 768w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 500px) 100vw, 500px\" /></p>\n<p><strong>相关阅读：</strong></p>\n<blockquote class=\"wp-embedded-content\" data-secret=\"Uf8efQ4fUh\"><p><a href=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/2019/02/%e3%80%90%e7%ab%8b%e6%ad%a4%e5%ad%98%e7%85%a7%e3%80%91%e5%ad%a6%e6%a0%a1%e4%b9%9f%e4%b8%8d%e6%98%af%e6%b3%95%e5%a4%96%e4%b9%8b%e5%9c%b0-%e5%b0%86%e7%bb%99%e4%ba%88%e7%ba%aa%e5%be%8b%e5%a4%84%e5%88%86/\">【立此存照】学校也不是法外之地 将给予纪律处分</a></p></blockquote>\n<p><iframe class=\"wp-embedded-content\" sandbox=\"allow-scripts\" security=\"restricted\" style=\"position: absolute; clip: rect(1px, 1px, 1px, 1px);\" src=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/2019/02/%e3%80%90%e7%ab%8b%e6%ad%a4%e5%ad%98%e7%85%a7%e3%80%91%e5%ad%a6%e6%a0%a1%e4%b9%9f%e4%b8%8d%e6%98%af%e6%b3%95%e5%a4%9